    {
      "text": "Buzz Lightyear of Star Command is a Windows PC game created by Traveller's Tales with Disney Interactive and PIXAR in 2000. The game consists of multiple planets, each with a villain on it. In each level, the players race the villain to their getaway destination. Then, they engage in a one-on-one battle with the villain, which usually requires destroying an energy shield surrounding the villain.",
